There are 2 major modes for editing the keyboard macro scripting language [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autohotkey Autohotkey].

One is [http://www.robf.de/Hacking/elisp/ahk-mode.el ahk-mode] by Robert Widhopf-Fenk. This one is bundled with the AutoHotKey software.

Another one is [http://xahlee.org/mswin/emacs_autohotkey_mode.html xahk-mode] by Xah Lee.

: <em>Note that as of mid-2014, Xah Lee has started charging money (US$5.00) for xahk-mode.</em>
